---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Privacy-First Data Linking at Scale | Case Study">
  <div class="project-detail-bg">
    <div class="project-detail-card">
      <a href="/case-studies" class="back-button">&larr; Back to Case Studies</a>
      <div class="project-detail-content">
        <h1>How We Linked 4.8 Billion Records Without Exposing a Single Patient</h1>
        <p class="summary">
          Our client needed to enable cross-organization analytics on clinical
          data — but couldn't share any personally identifiable information.
          We built a privacy-first tokenization pipeline that made it possible.
        </p>

        <h2>The Challenge</h2>
        <p>
          Pharma analytics requires linking data across organizations to get
          meaningful insights. But with HIPAA requirements, sharing patient
          identifiers is a non-starter. The client needed a way to link records
          across boundaries without ever exposing PII.
        </p>

        <h2>What We Built</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Registered and configured the tokenization application, mapping
            PII columns and defining output schemas for secure token creation.
          </li>
          <li>
            Worked directly with the tokenization vendor (Datavant) throughout
            platform configuration and troubleshooting.
          </li>
          <li>
            Developed secure SQL and Snowflake pipelines for partitioned
            (daily/monthly) tokenization runs with full auditability.
          </li>
          <li>
            Ran comprehensive validation to ensure each token mapped correctly
            while all PII was properly excluded.
          </li>
          <li>
            Set up centralized token distribution tables for clients and
            partner platforms.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Data Integrity & Privacy</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Maintained strict compliance — unique identifiers preserved for
            research, all required PII excluded.
          </li>
          <li>
            Systematic QA of all outputs, protecting patient privacy while
            enabling high-value pharma analytics.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Results</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>4.8 billion records</strong> tokenized with full privacy
            compliance.
          </li>
          <li>
            Reduced implementation friction through collaborative vendor
            engagement and rapid troubleshooting.
          </li>
          <li>
            Enabled partner overlap analytics across organizational boundaries
            — unlocking new revenue streams for the client.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="tech-stack-detail">
          <strong>Tech:</strong>
          <span>Datavant</span>
          <span>SQL</span>
          <span>Snowflake</span>
          <span>Data Portal Integration</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .project-detail-bg {
      min-height: 100vh;
      width: 100vw;
      background:
        linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.78), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)),
        url("/images/case_studies_tech.png") no-repeat center center;
      background-size: cover;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: center;
      padding-top: 72px;
    }
    .project-detail-card {
      max-width: 830px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      width: 100%;
      background: rgba(25, 30, 55, 0.68);
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 48px 40px 52px 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 44px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.13);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px) saturate(130%);
    }
    .back-button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #2997ff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .back-button:hover {
      color: #147bcd;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .project-detail-content {
      color: #f5f5f7;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #2997ff;
      font-size: 2.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
    }
    .summary {
      font-size: 1.13rem;
      color: #f5f5f7;
      margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: #d2d2d7;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 1.18rem;
      color: #79bbff;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    ul {
      margin: 0;
      margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
      padding-left: 1.2em;
    }
    ul li {
      font-size: 1.07rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.24em;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .tech-stack-detail {
      margin-top: 2.2rem;
      padding: 0.7rem 0.9rem;
      background: rgba(41, 151, 255, 0.09);
      border-radius: 13px;
      font-size: 1.02rem;
      color: #2997ff;
      font-weight: 500;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .tech-stack-detail strong {
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-right: 10px;
      color: #147bcd;
    }
    @media (max-width: 800px) {
      .project-detail-card {
        padding: 20px 8px 22px 8px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</MainLayout>
